<figureCitation box="[630,654,1934,1960]" captionStart="FIGURE 11" captionStartId="14.[151,250,1036,1060]" captionTargetBox="[153,1435,183,1013]" captionTargetId="figure-23@14.[151,1437,181,1013]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 11. Inthaeron longipes (Gravely, 1931) comb. nov., left pedipalp of syntype Ƌ of Sphingius longipes Gravely, 1931.A prolateral. B ventral. C retrolateral. Abbreviations: E embolus, FF fringed flange, RTA retrolateral tibial apophysis. Scale bars: A–C, 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4387703" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4387703/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="516">11</figureCitation>
