<bibRefCitation author="Platnick, N. I. &amp; Gajbe, U. A." box="[772,1031,1934,1960]" pageId="11" pageNumber="516" pagination="82 - 83" refId="ref7616" refString="Platnick, N. I. &amp; Gajbe, U. A. (1994) Supplementary notes on the ground spider family Cithaeronidae (Araneae, Gnaphosoidea). Journal of Arachnology, 22, 82 - 83." type="journal article" year="1994">Platnick &amp; Gajbe 1994</bibRefCitation>
